File->Print

This is used to print a hard copy of the Movieola scene. "Painters Action"
is used to create the PostScript file used for printing. The PostScript
file created is sent to the default printer (pointed to by the PRINTER
environment variable in your shell).

To send to another printer (say "myPrinter"), before you startup Movieola,
please set the following environment variable on your console.

setenv PRINTER  myPrinter
